<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajanduse seadus </eesti>
<inglise>Organic Farming Act </inglise>
<eesti>Vastu v&otilde;etud 11. aprillil 2001. a. </eesti>
<inglise>Passed 11 April 2001 </inglise>
<eesti>(RT I 2001, 42, 235), </eesti>
<inglise>(RT (1) I 2001, 42, 235), </inglise>
<eesti>j&otilde;ustunud 1. mail 2001. a. </eesti>
<inglise>entered into force 1 May 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;ldosa </eesti>
<inglise>General Part </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse reguleerimisala </eesti>
<inglise>Scope of application of Act </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esolev seadus kehtestab mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitavalt m&auml;rgistada kavatsetava p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse tootmisele ja selliselt m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete k&auml;itlemisele esitatavad n&otilde;uded, samuti j&auml;relevalve korra mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku tootmise ja k&auml;itlemise &uuml;le ning vastutuse k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete rikkumise korral. </eesti>
<inglise>This Act establishes the requirements for the production of agricultural produce intended to bear labelling referring to organic production methods, the requirements for the handling of agricultural produce and products which bear labelling referring to such methods, the inspection system for organic production and handling, and liability in the event of a violation of the requirements of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandus </eesti>
<inglise>Organic farming </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajandus on keskkonda s&auml;&auml;stev ja looduslikku tasakaalu s&auml;ilitav p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste tootmine ning p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete k&auml;itlemine, mis vastab k&auml;esoleva seaduse ning teiste p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste tootmist ning p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete k&auml;itlemist reguleerivate seaduste ja nende alusel kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktide n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Organic farming is the sustainable production of agricultural produce and the sustainable handling of agricultural produce and products which maintains basic equilibria and which is carried out in compliance with this Act, with other Acts regulating the production of agricultural produce and the handling of agricultural produce and products, and with legislation established on the basis thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Geneetiliselt muundatud organismide, nendest koosnevate v&otilde;i neid sisaldavate toodete, mille kasutamist reguleerib geneetiliselt muundatud organismide keskkonda viimise seadus (RT I 1999, 10, 151; 2001, 23, 130), samuti geneetiliselt muundatud organismidest v&otilde;i nende abil saadud, kuid geneetiliselt muundatud organisme mittesisaldavate toodete ehk geneetiliselt muundatud organismide derivaatide ning ioniseeriva kiirguse kasutamine mahep&otilde;llumajanduses on keelatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The use of genetically modified organisms and products composed of or containing such organisms, as regulated by the Deliberate Release of Genetically Modified Organisms into the Environment Act (RT I 1999, 10, 151; 2001, 23, 130), the use of derivatives of genetically modified organisms, meaning products which are derived from or with the aid of genetically modified organisms but which do not contain genetically modified organisms, and the use of ionising radiation in organic farming are prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>P&otilde;llumajandussaadus ja p&otilde;llumajandustootja </eesti>
<inglise>Agricultural produce and agricultural producer </inglise>
<eesti>(1) P&otilde;llumajandussaadus k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on t&ouml;&ouml;tlemata v&otilde;i esmat&ouml;&ouml;deldud taime- v&otilde;i loomakasvatussaadus, mida kasutatakse naturaalselt v&otilde;i p&otilde;llumajandustoote valmistamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, agricultural produce is the unprocessed produce of or prepared produce from crop production or livestock farming, used either in its natural state or for the manufacture of agricultural products. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Taimekasvatussaadus k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on taimsete saaduste tootmise eesm&auml;rgil kasvatatav taim, seen v&otilde;i nende saadus, samuti loodusest korjatud taim, seen v&otilde;i nende saadus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, plant produce is a plant or mushroom grown with the objective of producing products of plant origin, or produce derived from such plant or mushroom, or a plant or mushroom collected from its natural habitat, or produce derived from such plant or mushroom. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Loomakasvatussaadus k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on loomsete saaduste tootmise eesm&auml;rgil peetav loom v&otilde;i loomne saadus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) For the purposes of this Act, a livestock product is an animal kept with the objective of producing products of animal origin, or a product of animal origin. </inglise>
<eesti>Vabalt looduses kasvanud loomade seast k&uuml;titud v&otilde;i p&uuml;&uuml;tud looma v&otilde;i selle saadust ei loeta loomakasvatussaaduseks. </eesti>
<inglise>An animal hunted or caught while living freely in the wild or produce derived from such animal is not deemed to be a livestock product. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) P&otilde;llumajandustootja (edaspidi tootja) k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on isik, kes tegeleb p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste tootmisega ja samas ettev&otilde;ttes v&otilde;i selle osas (edaspidi ettev&otilde;te) toodetud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja turustamisega. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) For the purposes of this Act, an agricultural producer (hereinafter producer) is a person who engages in the production of agricultural produce, and the preparation and marketing of agricultural produce produced in the same enterprise or a part thereof (hereinafter enterprise). </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Saaduse esmat&ouml;&ouml;tlemine k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on saaduse puhastamine, sorteerimine, t&uuml;keldamine, kuivatamine, jahutamine, jahvatamine, pakendamine, m&auml;rgistamine v&otilde;i muu sarnasel viisil t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) For the purposes of this Act, the preparation of agricultural produce is the cleaning, sorting, cutting, drying, cooling, grinding, packing, labelling or other similar processing of the produce. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>P&otilde;llumajandustoode ja k&auml;itleja </eesti>
<inglise>Agricultural product and handler </inglise>
<eesti>(1) P&otilde;llumajandustoode k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise tulemusena valminud toit v&otilde;i s&ouml;&ouml;t. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, agricultural products are foodstuffs and animal feedingstuffs resulting from the processing of agricultural produce and products. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;itleja k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on isik, kes tegeleb p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja turustamisega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, a handler is a person who is engaged in the processing and marketing of agricultural produce and products. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;itlejaks k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses ei loeta: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) For the purposes of this Act, the following are not deemed to be handlers: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tootjat; </eesti>
<inglise>1) producers; </inglise>
<eesti>2) isikut, kes tegeleb mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitavalt m&auml;rgistatud m&uuml;&uuml;gipakendis p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete turustamisega. </eesti>
<inglise>2) persons who are engaged in the marketing of agricultural produce and products in sales packaging with labelling referring to organic production methods. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitav p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote m&auml;rgistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Labelling of organic produce and products with reference to organic production methods </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitav m&auml;rgistamine on p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote t&auml;histamine k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel kehtestatud mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitava m&auml;rgiga (edaspidi mahem&auml;rk) v&otilde;i s&otilde;naga p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote pinnal, pakendil, etiketil, saatedokumendil v&otilde;i mujal, samuti tarbija muul viisil teavitamine sellest, et p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse tootmine ning p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse ja -toote k&auml;itlemine vastab k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Labelling referring to organic production methods means the marking of organic produce and products with a label established on the basis of this Act (hereinafter ecolabel) or word referring to organic production methods which is attached to the surface, packaging, label or accompanying document of agricultural produce and products or elsewhere, and the giving of information to consumers in any other manner that given agricultural produce has been produced or that given agricultural produce or a given agricultural product has been handled in accordance with the requirements of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) S&otilde;naga "mahe" v&otilde;i liits&otilde;naga, mille esimene osa on "mahe", ei tohi m&auml;rgistada p&otilde;llumajandussaadusi ega -tooteid, mis on toodetud v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;deldud ettev&otilde;ttes, mis ei vasta k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele, v&auml;lja arvatud juhul, kui s&otilde;na "mahe" kirjeldab p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote maitse- v&otilde;i muid sarnaseid omadusi ning on selgelt arusaadav, et s&otilde;na "mahe" ei osuta p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikule tootmisele ega t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisele. (3) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitavalt m&auml;rgistada kavatsetava v&otilde;i m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse ja -toote tootmisel, veol ja turustamisel tuleb &auml;ra hoida selle segunemine mittemahep&otilde;llumajandusliku saaduse ja tootega ning tagada nende eristatavus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The word "mahe" [ organic ] or a compound word the first part of which is "mahe" shall not be used for the labelling of agricultural produce or products which have been produced or processed in an enterprise which does not meet the requirements of this Act, except in cases where the word "mahe" (2) describes the flavour or other similar characteristics of agricultural produce or an agricultural product and where it is evident that the word "mahe" does not refer to organic production or processing methods. (3) Upon the production, transportation and marketing of agricultural produce and products which bear or are intended to bear labelling referring to organic production methods, such produce and products shall be prevented from being mixed with agricultural produce and products which have been obtained by conventional production methods, and it shall be ensured that both groups of products and produce are distinguishable from one another. </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>P&otilde;llumajandussaaduste mahep&otilde;llumajanduslik tootmine ja k&auml;itlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Organic production and handling of agricultural produce </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajanduslik taimekasvatus </eesti>
<inglise>Organic plant production </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajanduslik taimekasvatus on taimekasvatussaaduste tootmine koosk&otilde;las k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Organic plant production is the production of plant produce in accordance with the requirements of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;uded kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the requirements for organic plant production. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;uded sisaldavad: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The requirements for organic plant production shall include: </inglise>
<eesti>1) mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse &uuml;ldn&otilde;udeid; </eesti>
<inglise>1) general requirements for organic plant production; </inglise>
<eesti>2) n&otilde;udeid ettev&otilde;ttele, kus tegeldakse mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatusega, ja tingimusi, mille korral v&otilde;ib muuta &uuml;leminekuaja kestust; </eesti>
<inglise>2) requirements for enterprises engaged in organic plant production and the conditions upon the existence of which the duration of the conversion period may be modified; </inglise>
<eesti>3) n&otilde;udeid seente kasvatamiseks kasutatava kasvusubstraadi kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>3) requirements for the substrates used for the production of mushrooms; </inglise>
<eesti>4) n&otilde;udeid mitteharitavate alade kohta, kust v&otilde;ib korjata taimi ja seeni; </eesti>
<inglise>4) requirements for areas not under cultivation where plants and mushrooms may be collected; </inglise>
<eesti>5) n&otilde;udeid kasutatava seemne ja taimse paljundusmaterjali kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>5) requirements for seed and vegetative propagating material; </inglise>
<eesti>6) v&auml;etamiseks ning umbrohu ja taimekahjustajate t&otilde;rjeks kasutada lubatud ainete loetelu ning kasutamise tingimusi. </eesti>
<inglise>6) a list of substances permitted for fertilisation and weed and plant pest control, and the conditions for their use. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;leminek mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikule taimekasvatusele </eesti>
<inglise>Conversion to organic plant production </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;leminekuaja kestus mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikus taimekasvatuses on kasutatava p&otilde;llumajandusmaa puhul kaks aastat ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse saamisele j&auml;rgnenud esimesest k&uuml;lvist arvates ja mitmeaastaste taimede kasvatamiseks kasutatava p&otilde;llumajandusmaa (v&auml;lja arvatud rohumaa) puhul kolm aastat ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse saamisele j&auml;rgnenud esmasest saagikoristusest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The duration of the conversion period to organic plant production in the case of agricultural land being used is two years as of the first sowing following the obtaining of approval for the enterprise, and in the case of agricultural land being used for the growing of perennial crops (except grasslands), the duration of the conversion period is three years after the first harvest following the obtaining of approval for the enterprise. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalveasutus v&otilde;ib mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;uetes loetletud tingimustel &uuml;leminekuaja kestust muuta. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The inspection authority has the right to modify the duration of the conversion period under the conditions specified in the requirements for organic plant production. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>Seeme ja taimne paljundusmaterjal </eesti>
<inglise>Seed and vegetative propagating material </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikus taimekasvatuses peab kasutama mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikult toodetud seemet ja taimset paljundusmaterjali. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Only seed and vegetative propagating material produced by organic production methods shall be used in organic plant production. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalveasutus v&otilde;ib mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;uetes loetletud tingimustel lubada mittemahep&otilde;llumajanduslikult toodetud seemne ja taimse paljundusmaterjali kasutamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The inspection authority may, under the conditions listed in the requirements set for organic plant production, permit the use of seed and vegetative propagating material which has been obtained by conventional production methods. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajanduslik loomakasvatus </eesti>
<inglise>Organic livestock production </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajanduslik loomakasvatus on loomakasvatussaaduste tootmine koosk&otilde;las k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Organic livestock production is the production of animal produce in accordance with the requirements of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse n&otilde;uded kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the requirements for organic livestock production. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse n&otilde;uded sisaldavad: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The requirements for organic livestock production shall include: </inglise>
<eesti>1) mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse &uuml;ldn&otilde;udeid; </eesti>
<inglise>1) general requirements for organic livestock production; </inglise>
<eesti>2) n&otilde;udeid ettev&otilde;ttele, kus tegeldakse mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatusega, ja &uuml;leminekuaja kestust s&otilde;ltuvalt kasvatatavast loomaliigist; </eesti>
<inglise>2) requirements for enterprises engaged in organic livestock production, and the duration of the conversion period depending on the animal species reared; </inglise>
<eesti>3) n&otilde;udeid loomade p&auml;ritolu, veo, s&ouml;&ouml;da ja s&ouml;&ouml;tmise, loomakasvatusv&otilde;tete, haiguste ennetamise ja veterinaarravi kohta, samuti mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikus loomakasvatuses kasutada lubatud s&ouml;&ouml;tade, s&ouml;&ouml;dalisandite ja abiainete ning loomakasvatusehitiste ja seadmete puhastamiseks ja desinfitseerimiseks lubatud ainete loetelu; </eesti>
<inglise>3) requirements for the origin, transportation, feedingstuffs and feeding of animals, husbandry management practices, disease prevention and veterinary treatment, and for the feedingstuffs, feed additives and processing aids permitted in organic livestock production, and a list of the substances permitted for the cleaning and disinfection of livestock buildings and of farm equipment; </inglise>
<eesti>4) n&otilde;udeid, millele peavad vastama loomakasvatushooned, -rajatised ja jalutusalad, ning lubatud loomade arvu pinna&uuml;hiku kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>4) requirements for livestock buildings, constructions and exercise areas for livestock, and the number of animals permitted per surface unit; </inglise>
<eesti>5) n&otilde;udeid s&otilde;nniku hoidmise ja kasutamise kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>5) requirements for the storage and use of manure; </inglise>
<eesti>6) mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku mesinduse &uuml;ldn&otilde;udeid, n&otilde;udeid &uuml;leminekuajal oleva ettev&otilde;tte kohta ja &uuml;leminekuaja kestust, n&otilde;udeid mesilaste p&auml;ritolu, mesila asukoha, tarude, mesilaste s&ouml;&ouml;da ja s&ouml;&ouml;tmise kohta ning mesindusv&otilde;tete ja veterinaarravi kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>6) general requirements for organic beekeeping, requirements for enterprises during the conversion period and the duration of the conversion period, requirements for the origin of bees, location of apiaries, beehives, feed and feeding of bees, beekeeping management practices and veterinary treatment; </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatusega tegelev isik peab lisaks mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse n&otilde;uetele j&auml;rgima ka mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;udeid. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) In addition to adhering to the requirements for organic livestock production, a person engaged in organic livestock production shall also adhere to the requirements for organic plant production. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajanduslik t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Organic processing </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitavalt m&auml;rgistatud (edaspidi m&auml;rgistatud) p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel v&otilde;ib juhul, kui tooteid kavatsetakse turustada m&auml;rgistatud toodetena, kasutada ainult lubatud mittemahep&otilde;llumajandusliku p&auml;ritoluga koostisosi ja mittep&otilde;llumajanduslikke koostisosi ning mahep&otilde;llumajanduslike koostisosade t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks v&otilde;ib kasutada ainult lubatud abiaineid, mikroorganisme ja ens&uuml;&uuml;me. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Upon the processing of agricultural produce and products labelled with a reference to organic production methods (hereinafter labelled) and in cases where the products are intended to be marketed as labelled products, only such ingredients obtained by conventional production methods as are permitted and such ingredients of non-agricultural origin as are permitted may be used, and only such processing aids, micro-organisms and enzymes as are permitted may be used for the processing of ingredients obtained by organic production methods. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise n&otilde;uded kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the requirements for organic processing. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise n&otilde;uded sisaldavad m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel kasutada lubatud mittemahep&otilde;llumajandusliku p&auml;ritoluga koostisosade ja mittep&otilde;llumajanduslike koostisosade loetelu, p&otilde;llumajanduslike koostisosade t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks kasutada lubatud abiainete, mikroorganismide ja ens&uuml;&uuml;mide loetelu ja kasutamise tingimusi ning muid t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise n&otilde;udeid. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The requirements for organic processing shall include a list of ingredients obtained by conventional production methods and ingredients of non-agricultural origin which are permitted in the processing of labelled agricultural produce and products, a list of processing aids, micro-organisms and enzymes which are permitted in the processing of ingredients obtained by organic production methods, and other processing requirements. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;itleja, kes t&ouml;&ouml;tleb m&auml;rgistatud ning m&auml;rgistamata p&otilde;llumajandussaadusi v&otilde;i -tooteid samas ettev&otilde;ttes, peab tagama nende eristatavuse ning &auml;ra hoidma nende segunemise, samuti peab ta tagama t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise tulemusena valminud ja m&auml;rgistada kavatsetavate toodete eristatavuse ja &auml;ra hoidma nende segunemise mittemahep&otilde;llumajanduslike toodetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A handler who processes both labelled and unlabelled agricultural produce and products in the same enterprise shall ensure that both classes of produce and products are distinguishable from one another and shall prevent from their being mixed, and shall ensure that products which are prepared as a result of processing and which are to be labelled are distinguishable from products obtained by conventional production methods and shall prevent both groups of products from being mixed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote turustamine </eesti>
<inglise>Marketing of labelled agricultural produce and products </inglise>
<eesti>(1) M&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote turustamine k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote ladustamine, Eestisse sissevedu ja Eestist v&auml;ljavedu, m&uuml;&uuml;giks pakkumine, m&uuml;&uuml;mine ja muul viisil tasuta v&otilde;i tasu eest &uuml;leandmine. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, the marketing of labelled agricultural produce and products is the storage, import into Estonia, export from Estonia, offer for sale, sale, and transfer in any other manner, without charge or for a charge, of labelled agricultural produce and products. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) M&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote turustamisel peab turustamisega tegelev isik: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A person engaged in the marketing of labelled agricultural produce and products shall: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tagama m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote ning m&auml;rgistamata p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote eristatavuse ja &auml;ra hoidma nende segunemise; </eesti>
<inglise>1) ensure that labelled agricultural produce and products are distinguishable from unlabelled agricultural produce and products, and shall prevent them from being mixed; </inglise>
<eesti>2) varustama kaubapartii tootja v&otilde;i viimase k&auml;itleja tuvastamist v&otilde;imaldavate dokumentidega. </eesti>
<inglise>2) supply each lot of goods with documentation which enables the producer or the last handler of the lot to be identified. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Isik, kes tegeleb m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete sisseveoga, peab olema kantud mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A person engaged in the import of labelled agricultural produce and products shall be entered in the register of organic farming. </inglise>
<eesti>Registrisse kandmiseks esitab isik mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registri volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejale taotluse koos registrisse kantavate andmetega, olles enne tasunud riigil&otilde;ivu registrisse kandmise eest. </eesti>
<inglise>In order to be entered in the register of organic farming, a person shall submit an application together with the information to be entered in the register to the authorised processor of the register, after having paid the state fee for entry into the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Sisse vedada ja m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -tootena v&otilde;ib turustada p&auml;ritolumaa n&otilde;uete kohaselt m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaadust v&otilde;i -toodet riikidest, mille mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku p&auml;ritoluga p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote tootmise ja k&auml;itlemise n&otilde;uded ning j&auml;relevalves&uuml;steem on tunnistatud koosk&otilde;las olevaks Eestis kehtivate n&otilde;uetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Agricultural produce and products may be imported into Estonia and marketed as labelled agricultural produce and products if they are labelled in accordance with the requirements of their state of origin and if the requirements for the production and handling of agricultural produce and products of organic origin and the inspection system in the given state have been declared to be in accordance with the corresponding requirements in force in Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Sisseveetava m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote partii peab olema varustatud p&auml;ritoluriigi p&auml;deva asutuse v&auml;ljastatud tunnistusega. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Each lot of imported labelled agricultural produce and products shall be supplied with a certificate issued by a competent authority of the state of origin. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote sisseveo tingimused ja korra kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the conditions and procedure for the import of labelled agricultural produce and products. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) V&auml;ljaveetava m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote partii kohta v&auml;ljastab m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote tunnistuse tootja, k&auml;itleja v&otilde;i v&auml;ljaveoga tegeleva isiku taotluse alusel k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 22 nimetatud p&auml;dev j&auml;relevalveasutus. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) On the application of a producer, handler or person engaged in the export of labelled agricultural produce or products, the inspection authority specified in &sect; 22 of this Act shall issue a certificate for each lot of labelled agricultural produce and products to be exported. </inglise>
<eesti>Tunnistuse sisu- ja vormin&otilde;uded ning v&auml;ljaandmise korra kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the substantive and formal requirements for the certificates and the procedure for the issue of the certificates. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistada kavatsetavate ja m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete vedu </eesti>
<inglise>Transportation of agricultural produce and products intended to be labelled and labelled agricultural produce and products </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistada kavatsetavate ja m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete veol tuleb tagada nende eristatavus ning &auml;ra hoida nende segunemine mittemahep&otilde;llumajanduslike saaduste v&otilde;i toodetega. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon the transportation of agricultural produce and products intended to be labelled and labelled agricultural produce and products, it shall be ensured that they are distinguishable from produce and products obtained by conventional production methods, and the different groups of produce and products shall be prevented from mixing. </inglise>
<eesti>3. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 3 </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustamine ning m&auml;rgistusluba </eesti>
<inglise>Approval of Enterprises and Labelling Authorisation </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustamine </eesti>
<inglise>Approval of enterprise </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Tunnustamine on menetlus, mille k&auml;igus k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 22 nimetatud p&auml;dev j&auml;relevalveasutus hindab ettev&otilde;tte tootmise v&otilde;i k&auml;itlemise vastavust k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Approval is a procedure during which the competent inspection authority specified in &sect; 22 of this Act evaluates the compliance of the production or handling carried out by an enterprise with the requirements of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tunnustamine viiakse l&auml;bi tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja esitatud vormikohase taotluse alusel p&auml;rast tunnustamise eest riigil&otilde;ivu tasumist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Approval is conducted on the basis of a standard format application submitted by a processor or handler and after the applicant has paid the state fee for approval. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse esitamise t&auml;htaja, taotluse vormi ning tunnustamise, tunnustatuse peatamise ja kehtetuks tunnistamise korra kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of the Agriculture shall establish the term for submission of applications, the format of applications and the procedure for approval and for suspension and revocation of approval. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui ettev&otilde;tte tootmine v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine vastab k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele, teeb j&auml;relevalveasutus taotluse saamisest arvates 20 t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul otsuse ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If the production or processing carried out by an enterprise complies with the requirements of this Act, the inspection authority shall make a decision concerning the grant of approval within twenty working days as of the date of receipt of the application. </inglise>
<eesti>Otsustamist&auml;htaega v&otilde;ib lisaasjaolude selgitamiseks pikendada kuni 60 t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise>In order to clarify additional circumstances, the term for making the decision may be extended by up to sixty working days. </inglise>
<eesti>T&auml;htaja pikendamisest teatatakse taotlejale kirjalikult. </eesti>
<inglise>The applicant shall be informed of the extension of the term in writing. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ettev&otilde;te loetakse tunnustatuks otsuse tegemise p&auml;evast arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) An enterprise is deemed to be approved as of the date on which the decision is made. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;te, kus tegeldakse mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku tootmisega ja mille tunnustamise taotlus on esitatud t&auml;htaegselt, loetakse tunnustatuks taotluse saamise p&auml;evast arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>An enterprise engaged in organic production which has submitted an application within the specified term is deemed to be approved as of the date on which the application is received. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja, kelle ettev&otilde;te on saanud tunnustatuse, kantakse mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registrisse j&auml;relevalveasutuse esitatud andmete alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A producer or handler whose enterprise has obtained approval shall be entered in the register of organic farming on the basis of information submitted by the inspection authority. </inglise>
<eesti>Teade tunnustatuse saamise kohta ja registrikande &auml;rakiri edastatakse taotlejale k&uuml;mne t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul otsuse tegemise p&auml;evast arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>A notice concerning the grant of approval and a copy of the register entry shall be sent to the applicant within ten working days as of the date on which the corresponding decision is made. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kui tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja ei ole esitanud k&otilde;iki k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud andmeid, kui ta on esitanud valeandmeid v&otilde;i kui ettev&otilde;te ei vasta k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele, teeb j&auml;relevalveasutus kirjaliku p&otilde;hjendatud otsuse ettev&otilde;tte n&otilde;uetele mittevastavuse kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If a producer or handler fails to submit all the information provided for in this Act or submits false information or if an enterprise does not comply with the requirements of this Act, the inspection authority shall make a reasoned written decision concerning the non-compliance of the enterprise with the requirements. </inglise>
<eesti>Otsuse &auml;rakiri edastatakse taotlejale ja mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registri volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejale k&uuml;mne t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul otsuse tegemise p&auml;evast arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>A copy of the decision shall be sent to the applicant and the authorised processor of the register of organic farming within ten working days as of the date on which the decision is made. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Tunnustatud ettev&otilde;tte omandi v&otilde;i valduse &uuml;leminekul peab omandaja v&otilde;i valduse saaja, kes soovib j&auml;tkata mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikku tootmist v&otilde;i k&auml;itlemist, esitama j&auml;relevalveasutusele hiljemalt omandi v&otilde;i valduse &uuml;lemineku p&auml;eval taotluse mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku tootmise v&otilde;i k&auml;itlemise j&auml;tkamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) Upon a transfer of ownership or possession of an approved enterprise or a part thereof, a transferee or recipient of possession who wishes to continue organic production or handling shall submit an application to the inspection authority for the continuation of organic production or handling not later than on the date of transfer of ownership or possession. </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Tunnustamise ajal valitsenud ehituslike, tehnoloogiliste ja muude sarnaste tingimuste muutumisest peab tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja teavitama j&auml;relevalveasutust seitsme p&auml;eva jooksul, kui mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse, mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse v&otilde;i mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise n&otilde;uetes ei ole ette n&auml;htud teavitamise teistsugust t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) A processor or handler shall inform the inspection authority of any changes to the construction, technological or other similar conditions which existed at the time of approval within seven days, unless the requirements for organic plant production, organic livestock production or organic processing prescribe a different term. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse peatamine </eesti>
<inglise>Suspension of approval of enterprise </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatus peatatakse, kui ettev&otilde;ttes valitsevate olude t&otilde;ttu ei ole v&otilde;imalik t&auml;ita k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;udeid. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The approval of an enterprise shall be suspended if the requirements of this Act cannot be complied with due to the circumstances prevailing in the enterprise. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tunnustatuse peatamiseks teeb tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja &uuml;le j&auml;relevalvet teostav j&auml;relevalveametnik ettekirjutuse. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In order to suspend approval, an official of the competent inspection authority shall issue a precept to this effect. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui tunnustatuse peatamise aluseks olnud asjaolud on k&otilde;rvaldatud, v&otilde;ib tunnustatuse peatamise j&auml;relevalveametniku otsusega l&otilde;petada. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Suspension of approval may be terminated on the decision of an official of the competent inspection authority if the circumstances on which the suspension of approval were based are eliminated. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 15. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 15. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Revocation of approval of enterprise </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalveasutus v&otilde;ib ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistada: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The inspection authority may revoke the approval of an enterprise: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja sellekohase taotluse alusel; </eesti>
<inglise>1) on the basis of an application to this effect submitted by the producer or handler; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kui tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja ei suuda ettev&otilde;ttes valitsevate p&uuml;siolude t&otilde;ttu t&auml;ita k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;udeid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) if the producer or handler is not able to comply with the requirements of this Act due to permanent circumstances prevailing in the enterprise; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kui tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja j&auml;tab kontrollimisel avastatud puudused m&auml;&auml;ratud ajaks k&otilde;rvaldamata; </eesti>
<inglise>3) if the producer or handler fails to eliminate the deficiencies discovered in the process of inspection by the specified date; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kui tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja ei esita j&auml;relevalveasutusele n&otilde;utavaid andmeid v&otilde;i takistab muul viisil j&auml;relevalve teostamist; </eesti>
<inglise>4) if the producer or handler fails to submit all the required information to the inspection authority or prevents inspection in any other manner; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kui tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja ei esita k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 16 l&otilde;ikes 5 s&auml;testatud kinnitust v&otilde;i ei ole tasunud riigil&otilde;ivu. </eesti>
<inglise>5) if the producer or handler does not submit the confirmation provided for in subsection 16 (5) of this Act or has not paid the state fee. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ettepaneku ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamiseks teeb tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja &uuml;le j&auml;relevalvet teostav j&auml;relevalveametnik j&auml;relevalveasutuse peadirektorile, kes teeb vastava otsuse ettepaneku saamisest arvates kolme t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The official carrying out the inspection of a producer or handler shall submit a proposal to revoke the approval of an enterprise to the Director General of the inspection authority, who shall make a corresponding decision within three working days as of the receipt of the proposal. </inglise>
<eesti>Tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamise kirjaliku otsuse &auml;rakiri edastatakse tootjale v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejale viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul otsuse tegemise p&auml;evast arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>A copy of the written decision to revoke the approval shall be forwarded to the producer or handler within five working days as of the date on which the decision is made. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamise otsusest teavitab j&auml;relevalveasutus viivitamata teisi k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 22 nimetatud j&auml;relevalveasutusi, mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registri volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejat ja Tarbijakaitseametit. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The inspection authority shall immediately inform the other competent inspection authorities specified in &sect; 22 of this Act, the authorised processor of the register of organic farming and the Consumer Protection Board of any decision to revoke approval. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja, kelle ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatus on kehtetuks tunnistatud k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 punktide 2 kuni 4 alusel, v&otilde;ib esitada tunnustamiseks uue taotluse, kui tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamise aluseks olnud asjaolud on k&otilde;rvaldatud, kuid mitte enne &uuml;he aasta m&ouml;&ouml;dumist tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamise otsuse tegemisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If the approval of the enterprise of a processor or handler is revoked on the basis of clauses (1) 2) -4) of this Act, the processor or handler has the right to submit a new application for approval if the circumstances on which revocation of the approval was based are eliminated, but not before one year has passed since the decision was made to revoke the approval. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 16. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 16. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajanduse register </eesti>
<inglise>Register of organic farming </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Mahep&otilde;llumajanduse register (edaspidi register) on riiklik register, mille p&otilde;llumajandusministri ettepanekul asutab ja mille p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;ruse kinnitab Vabariigi Valitsus andmekogude seaduses (RT I 1997, 28, 423; 1998, 36/37, 552; 1999, 10, 155; 2000, 50, 317; 57, 373; 92, 597; 2001, 7, 17; 17, 77) kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The register of organic farming (hereinafter register) is a state register which is established by the Government of the Republic on the proposal of the Minister of Agriculture and the statutes of which are approved by the Government of the Republic pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Databases Act (RT I 1997, 28, 423; 1998, 36/37, 552; 1999, 10, 155; 2000, 50, 317; 57, 373; 92, 597; 2001, 7, 17; 17, 77). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registri vastutav t&ouml;&ouml;tleja on P&otilde;llumajandusministeerium ja volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tleja Taimetoodangu Inspektsioon. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The chief processor of the register is the Ministry of Agriculture and the authorised processor of the register is the Plant Production Inspectorate. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registrisse kantakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The following shall be entered in the register: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja nimi, elu- v&otilde;i asukoht, postiaadress, isiku- v&otilde;i registrikood ja sidevahendite numbrid; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name, residence or location, postal address, personal identification code or registry code, and telecommunications numbers of the producer or handler; </inglise>
<eesti>2) ettev&otilde;tte asukoht, volitatud isiku nimi, postiaadress ja sidevahendite numbrid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the location of the enterprise, the name of the authorised person, and the postal address and telecommunications numbers of the enterprise; </inglise>
<eesti>3) andmed k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-de 13 kuni 15 alusel tehtud otsuste kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>3) information concerning decisions made on the basis of &sect;&sect; 13 to 15 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>4) &uuml;leminekuaja alguse kuup&auml;ev ja kestus; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the date of the beginning of the conversion period and its duration; </inglise>
<eesti>5) m&auml;rgistusloa v&auml;ljaandmise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the date on which labelling authorisation is issued; </inglise>
<eesti>6) andmed k&otilde;lvikute ja neil kasvatatavate taimeliikide kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>6) information concerning land use on parcels and the plant species grown; </inglise>
<eesti>7) andmed kasvatatavate loomaliikide kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>7) information concerning the animal species reared; </inglise>
<eesti>8) andmed k&auml;ideldavate tootegruppide kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>8) information concerning the product groups handled; </inglise>
<eesti>9) andmed tootja ettev&otilde;tte kontrollimise kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>9) information concerning the inspection of the producer's enterprise; </inglise>
<eesti>10) muud vajalikud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>10) other necessary information. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registri andmed on ristkasutuses andmetega, mis sisalduvad teistes andmekogudes, mille vastutavaks t&ouml;&ouml;tlejaks on P&otilde;llumajandusministeerium. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Data in the register is in interbase cross-usage with data stored in other databases the chief processor of which is the Ministry of Agriculture. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registrisse kantud tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja peab esitama jooksva aasta 10. detsembriks registri volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejale kirjaliku kinnituse mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku tegevuse j&auml;tkamise kohta j&auml;rgmisel aastal. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A producer or handler who is entered in the register shall submit written confirmation concerning the continuation of organic farming activities during the following year by 10 December of the current year to the authorised processor of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>T&auml;htp&auml;evaks kinnituse esitamata j&auml;tmise korral kustutatakse m&auml;rgistatud saaduste sisseveoga tegelev isik registrist v&otilde;i tunnistatakse ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatus kehtetuks alates j&auml;rgmise aasta 1. jaanuarist. </eesti>
<inglise>A person engaged in the import of labelled produce shall be deleted from the register and approval granted to an enterprise shall be revoked as of 1 January of the following year if the confirmation is not submitted by the specified date. </inglise>
<eesti>Registrisse kantud tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja peab tasuma riigil&otilde;ivu j&auml;relevalvetoimingute eest. </eesti>
<inglise>A producer or handler who is entered in the register shall pay the state fee for inspection operations. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 17. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 17. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistamise &otilde;igus ja m&auml;rgistusloa v&auml;ljaandmine </eesti>
<inglise>Right to label and issue of labelling authorisation </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Tootjal v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejal, kelle ettev&otilde;te on k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel tunnustatud ja kelle tegevus on k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete kohane, ning registrisse kantud sissevedajal, kelle tegevus on k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete kohane, on &otilde;igus p&otilde;llumajandussaadust v&otilde;i -toodet m&auml;rgistada vastavalt k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-des 19 kuni 21 s&auml;testatule. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Producers or handlers whose enterprise has been approved on the basis of this Act and whose activities are in compliance with the requirements of this Act and importers who are entered in the register and whose activities are in compliance with the requirements of this Act have the right to label agricultural produce and products pursuant to the provisions of &sect;&sect; 19 to 21 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja kasutatav m&auml;rgistus peab sisaldama ettev&otilde;tte &uuml;le j&auml;relevalvet teostava j&auml;relevalveasutuse nime v&otilde;i koodi. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Labelling used by a producer or handler shall include the name or code of the inspection authority which inspects the enterprise. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalveasutuse koodi m&auml;&auml;rab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of Agriculture shall determine the codes of inspection authorities. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Tootjal v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejal on &otilde;igus taotleda j&auml;relevalveasutuselt m&auml;rgistusloa v&auml;ljaandmist. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A producer or handler has the right to make an application for labelling authorisation to the inspection authority. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistusluba on dokument, mis t&otilde;endab tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud &otilde;igust. </eesti>
<inglise>Labelling authorisation is a document which certifies that the producer or handler has the right provided for in subsection (1) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistusloa annab j&auml;relevalve tulemuste p&otilde;hjal v&auml;lja j&auml;relevalveasutus, kelle p&auml;devusse kuulub ettev&otilde;tte tunnustamine. </eesti>
<inglise>The inspection authority which is competent to authorise enterprises shall issue labelling authorisation on the basis of the inspection results. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) M&auml;rgistusloa taotlemise ja v&auml;ljaandmise korra ning m&auml;rgistusloa vormi kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the procedure for the application for and issue of labelling authorisation and the format thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 18. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 18. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistamise &otilde;iguse peatumine ja l&otilde;ppemine </eesti>
<inglise>Suspension and extinguishment of right to label </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse peatamise korral peab tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja viivitamata m&auml;rgistamise katkestama kuni tunnustatuse peatamise l&otilde;petamiseni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If the approval granted to an enterprise is suspended, the producer or handler shall immediately discontinue labelling until such time as the suspension of approval is terminated. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalveametnik v&otilde;ib tootjale v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejale teha ettekirjutuse m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste v&otilde;i -toodete turustamise l&otilde;petamise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>An official of the competent inspection authority may issue a precept to a producer or handler for termination of the marketing of labelled agricultural produce and products. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse kehtetuks tunnistamise korral peab tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja m&auml;rgistamise ja m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete turustamise viivitamata l&otilde;petama. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A producer or handler shall immediately terminate labelling and the marketing of labelled agricultural produce and products if the approval granted to the enterprise is revoked. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 19. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 19. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;leminekuaja l&auml;binud ettev&otilde;ttes toodetud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse ja sellest valmistatud p&otilde;llumajandustoote m&auml;rgistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Labelling of agricultural produce produced in enterprise which has undergone conversion period and of products manufactured therefrom </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 5 s&auml;testatud viisil v&otilde;ib m&auml;rgistada p&otilde;llumajandussaadust, mis on toodetud &uuml;leminekuaja l&auml;binud ettev&otilde;ttes k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete kohaselt, v&otilde;i toiduks m&otilde;eldud p&otilde;llumajandustoodet, mida on t&ouml;&ouml;deldud k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete kohaselt ja mille p&otilde;llumajanduslikest koostisosadest v&auml;hemalt 95 protsenti on toodetud mahep&otilde;llumajanduslikule tootmisele &uuml;leminekuaja l&auml;binud ettev&otilde;ttes. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Agricultural produce which is produced in an enterprise which has undergone the conversion period in compliance with the requirements of this Act and agricultural products which are intended to be used as foodstuffs, which have been processed in compliance with the requirements of this Act and at least 95 per cent of the ingredients of agricultural origin in which have been produced in an enterprise which has undergone the conversion period to organic farming may be labelled in the manner provided in &sect; 5 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote t&auml;histamisel v&otilde;ib kasutada &uuml;ksnes mahem&auml;rki v&otilde;i s&otilde;na&uuml;hendit "kontrollitud mahep&otilde;llumajandusest", s&otilde;na "mahe" v&otilde;i liits&otilde;na, mille esimene osa on s&otilde;na "mahe". </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Only the ecolabel or the phrase "kontrollitud mahep&otilde;llumajandusest" [ inspected product, produced by organic farming methods ], the word "mahe" or a compound word the first word of which is "mahe" shall be used for labelling agricultural produce or products provided in subsection (1) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sisseveetud p&otilde;llumajandussaadust v&otilde;i -toodet, mis vastab k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud tingimustele ja on m&auml;rgistatud p&auml;ritoluriigi n&otilde;uete kohaselt, v&otilde;ib m&auml;rgistada k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 5 s&auml;testatud viisil, kasutades k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 esitatud t&auml;histust. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Imported agricultural produce or products which comply with the conditions provided for in subsection (1) of this section and are labelled according to the requirements of their state of origin may be labelled in the manner provided for in &sect; 5 of this Act, using the labelling set out in subsection (2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Mahem&auml;rgi etalonkirjelduse ja mahem&auml;rgi kasutamise korra kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Minister of Agriculture shall establish the standard description of the ecolabel and the procedure for the use thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 20. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 20. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;leminekuajal toodetud taimekasvatussaaduse ja sellest valmistatud toote m&auml;rgistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Labelling of plant produce produced during conversion period and of products manufactured therefrom </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;leminekuajal toodetud taimekasvatussaadust ja sellest valmistatud toodet v&otilde;ib m&auml;rgistada &uuml;ksnes s&otilde;na&uuml;hendiga "toodetud mahep&otilde;llumajandusele &uuml;lemineku ajal", kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Plant produce produced during the conversion period and products manufactured therefrom shall only be labelled with the phrase "toodetud mahep&otilde;llumajandusele &uuml;lemineku ajal" [ produced under conversion to organic farming ] if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) taimekasvatussaadus on toodetud ettev&otilde;ttes, mille &uuml;leminekuaeg on kestnud enne saagi koristamist v&auml;hemalt 12 kuud; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the plant produce is produced in an enterprise where the conversion period has lasted for at least twelve months before the harvesting of the crop; </inglise>
<eesti>2) p&otilde;llumajandustoote ainuke p&otilde;llumajanduslik koostisosa on k&auml;esoleva l&otilde;ike punkti 1 n&otilde;uetele vastav taimekasvatussaadus, mis on t&ouml;&ouml;deldud k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete kohaselt. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the only ingredient of agricultural origin in the agricultural product is plant produce which complies with the requirements of clause 1) of this subsection and which has been processed in compliance with the requirements of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) S&otilde;na&uuml;hendiga "toodetud mahep&otilde;llumajandusele &uuml;lemineku ajal" v&otilde;ib m&auml;rgistada sisseveetud taimekasvatussaadust v&otilde;i p&otilde;llumajandustoodet, mis vastab k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Imported plant produce or agricultural products which comply with the conditions set out in subsection (1) of this section may be labelled with the phrase "toodetud mahep&otilde;llumajandusele &uuml;lemineku ajal". </inglise>
<eesti>(3) M&auml;rgistus ei v&otilde;i suuruse, v&auml;rvuse ega tr&uuml;kikirja poolest olla erinev teistest p&otilde;llumajandussaadust v&otilde;i -toodet iseloomustavatest kirjetest. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The size, colour and printing of the labelling shall not differ from other labels which describe agricultural produce or an agricultural product. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 21. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 21. </inglise>
<eesti>Valdavalt mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku p&auml;ritoluga toote m&auml;rgistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Labelling of products of predominantly organic farming origin </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Toiduks m&otilde;eldud valdavalt mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku p&auml;ritoluga toodet v&otilde;ib m&auml;rgistada &uuml;ksnes s&otilde;na&uuml;hendiga &ldquo;... % p&otilde;llumajanduslikke koostisosi mahep&otilde;llumajandusest", kui toode on t&ouml;&ouml;deldud k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete kohaselt ja v&auml;hemalt 70 protsenti toote p&otilde;llumajanduslikest koostisosadest on toodetud &uuml;leminekuaja l&auml;binud ettev&otilde;ttes. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A product of predominantly organic farming origin may only be labelled with the phrase &ldquo;... % p&otilde;llumajanduslikke koostisosi mahep&otilde;llumajandusest" [... % of ingredients of agricultural origin produced by organic farming methods ] if the product has been processed in compliance with the requirements of this Act and if at least 70 per cent of the ingredients of agricultural origin of the product have been produced in an enterprise which has undergone the conversion period. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) S&otilde;na&uuml;hendiga &ldquo;... % p&otilde;llumajanduslikke koostisosi mahep&otilde;llumajandusest" v&otilde;ib m&auml;rgistada sisseveetud toodet, mis vastab k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Imported products which comply with the conditions set out in subsection (1) of this section may be marked with the phrase &ldquo;... % p&otilde;llumajanduslikke koostisosi mahep&otilde;llumajandusest". </inglise>
<eesti>(3) M&auml;rgistus ei v&otilde;i suuruse, v&auml;rvuse ega tr&uuml;kikirja poolest olla erinev teistest toodet iseloomustavatest kirjetest. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The size, colour and printing of the labelling shall not differ from other labels which describe a product. </inglise>
<eesti>4. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 4 </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve </eesti>
<inglise>Inspection System </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 22. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 22. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve </eesti>
<inglise>Inspection system </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalvet tootja ja m&auml;rgistatud taimekasvatussaaduste sisseveoga tegeleva isiku &uuml;le teostab Taimetoodangu Inspektsioon. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Plant Production Inspectorate is the competent authority responsible for the inspection of producers and persons engaged in the import of labelled plant produce. </inglise>
<eesti>Tootjaid &uuml;hendava mittetulundus&uuml;hingu kirjaliku soovi korral kutsub Taimetoodangu Inspektsioon mittetulundus&uuml;hingu liikmeks oleva tootja kohapealse kontrollimise juurde selle &uuml;hingu esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>At the written request of a non-profit association uniting the producers, the Plant Production Inspectorate shall invite a representative of the non-profit association to be present at the on-site inspection of a producer who is a member of such association. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalvet k&auml;itleja &uuml;le, kes tegeleb mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisega v&otilde;i m&auml;rgistatud loomakasvatussaaduste ja p&otilde;llumajandustoodete sisseveoga, teostab Veterinaar- ja Toiduamet. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Veterinary and Food Board is the competent authority responsible for the inspection of handlers engaged in organic processing or the import of labelled animal and agricultural products. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) J&auml;relevalvet k&auml;itleja &uuml;le, kes tegeleb m&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisega jaekaubandus- v&otilde;i toitlustusettev&otilde;ttes, teostab Tervisekaitseinspektsioon. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Health Protection Inspectorate is the competent authority responsible for the inspection of handlers engaged in the processing of labelled agricultural produce and products in retail establishments or mass caterers. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Tunnustatud ettev&otilde;tte vastavust k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele kontrollitakse kohapeal v&auml;hemalt kord aastas. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The compliance of approved enterprises with the requirements of this Act shall be inspected on site at least once a year. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 23. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 23. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalveametniku &otilde;igused ja kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Rights and duties of officials of competent inspection authorities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalveametnikul on &otilde;igus: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An official of a competent inspection authority has the right: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tootja, k&auml;itleja v&otilde;i tema esindaja juuresolekul takistamatult kontrollida k&auml;esoleva seaduse ja selle alusel kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktide n&otilde;uete j&auml;rgimist ettev&otilde;tte territooriumil ja ruumides; </eesti>
<inglise>1) to monitor, unhindered, compliance with the requirements of this Act and legislation established on the basis thereof on the territory and in the premises of an enterprise in the presence of the producer, handler or representative thereof; </inglise>
<eesti>2) saada tootjalt v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejalt vajalikku teavet, &auml;rakirju ja v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid asjakohastest dokumentidest, kaasa arvatud raamatupidamisdokumendid, j&auml;&auml;dvustada tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja teadmisel kontrollimise ajal valitsev olukord foto- v&otilde;i videotehnika abil; </eesti>
<inglise>(2) to obtain necessary information and copies or extracts of relevant documents, including accounting records, from a producer or handler, and, with the knowledge of the producer or handler, to record the situation at the time of the inspection with the aid of photographic or video equipment; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&otilde;tta n&otilde;uete rikkumise kahtluse korral tasuta kontrollproove, tellida ekspertiisi ja teha muid vajalikke toiminguid. </eesti>
<inglise>3) in the event of a suspected violation of the requirements, to take control samples without charge, order expert analyses and perform other necessary acts. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalveametnik on kohustatud: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An official of a competent inspection authority is required to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) hoidma talle teatavaks saanud &auml;risaladust; </eesti>
<inglise>1) maintain business secrets of which he or she becomes aware; </inglise>
<eesti>2) p&otilde;hjendama k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel tehtud otsust, vormistama selle kirjalikult; </eesti>
<inglise>2) provide reasons for a decision made on the basis of this Act and to formalise the decision in writing; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kandma kontrollimise ajal eri- v&otilde;i ametiriietust. </eesti>
<inglise>3) wear special clothing or professional attire during inspection. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutus </eesti>
<inglise>Precepts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Otilde;iguserikkumise avastamise korral teeb j&auml;relevalveametnik tootjale v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejale ettekirjutuse, millega: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Upon detection of an offence, an official of a competent inspection authority shall issue a precept to a producer or handler in which he or she shall: </inglise>
<eesti>1) juhib t&auml;helepanu &otilde;iguserikkumisele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) call attention to the offence; </inglise>
<eesti>2) n&otilde;uab &otilde;iguserikkumise l&otilde;petamist; </eesti>
<inglise>2) demand termination of the offence; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kohustab tegema vajalikke toiminguid &otilde;iguserikkumise l&otilde;petamiseks v&otilde;i edasiste &otilde;iguserikkumiste &auml;rahoidmiseks v&otilde;i peatab ettev&otilde;tte tunnustatuse; </eesti>
<inglise>3) require the performance of acts necessary for the termination of the offence or the prevention of future offences, or suspend the approval of the enterprise; </inglise>
<eesti>4) m&auml;&auml;rab ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmise t&auml;htaja. </eesti>
<inglise>4) set the term for compliance with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalveametnik teeb ettekirjutuse tootjale v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejale teatavaks allkirja vastu v&otilde;i saadab posti teel v&auml;ljastusteatega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An official of a competent inspection authority shall notify a producer or handler of a precept against a signature or shall send the precept by post with advice of delivery. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja ei n&otilde;ustu j&auml;relevalveametniku ettekirjutusega, v&otilde;ib ta esitada kaebuse asjaomase j&auml;relevalveasutuse peadirektorile ettekirjutusest teadasaamise p&auml;evast arvates viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If a producer or handler does not agree with a precept issued by an official of a competent inspection authority, the producer or handler may file a complaint with the Director General of the inspection authority concerned within five working days as of the date on which the producer or handler becomes aware of the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaebuse esitamine ei vabasta ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmisest. </eesti>
<inglise>The filing of an appeal does not release a person from compliance with the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) J&auml;relevalveasutuse peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja vaatab kaebuse l&auml;bi selle saamisest arvates viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Director General of an inspection authority or his or her deputy shall review a complaint within five working days as of the receipt thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>Lisaasjaolude selgitamiseks v&otilde;ib peadirektor otsuse tegemise t&auml;htaega pikendada kuni k&uuml;mme t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise>In order to clarify additional circumstances, the Director General may extend the term for making the decision to ten working days. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kaebust l&auml;bi vaadates teeb asjaomase j&auml;relevalveasutuse peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja otsuse j&auml;tta ettekirjutus j&otilde;usse, muuta v&otilde;i t&uuml;histada see ning teavitab tootjat v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejat oma otsusest kirjalikult. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) After reviewing a complaint, the Director General of the inspection authority concerned or his or her deputy shall make a decision to uphold, amend or repeal the precept and shall inform the producer or handler of the decision in writing. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) S&otilde;ltumata k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 5 alusel tehtud otsusest, on k&auml;itlejal &otilde;igus p&ouml;&ouml;rduda halduskohtusse. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) Regardless of a decision made pursuant to subsection (5) of this section, a handler has the right of recourse to an administrative court. </inglise>
<eesti>Halduskohtusse p&ouml;&ouml;rdumine ei vabasta tootjat v&otilde;i k&auml;itlejat ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmisest. </eesti>
<inglise>Recourse to an administrative court does not release a producer or handler from compliance with a precept. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) J&auml;relevalveametnik kontrollib ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmist. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) Officials of competent inspection authorities shall monitor compliance with precepts. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastutuse alused </eesti>
<inglise>Bases of liability </inglise>
<eesti>(1) F&uuml;&uuml;silised isikud vastutavad k&auml;esoleva seaduse ja selle alusel kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise eest haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 45, &otilde;iend; 58, 608; 60, 616; 87, 792; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301 ja 305; 51, 321; 54, 346, 348 ja 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544 ja 548; 89, 578; 95, 609 ja 613; 2001, 3, 5; 17, 76; 18, 87; 21, 115 ja 116; 31, 174) alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Natural persons are liable for violation of this Act and legislation established on the basis thereof on the basis of the Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 45, correction notice; 58, 608; 60, 616; 87, 792; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301 and 305; 51, 321; 54, 346, 348 and 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544 and 548; 89, 578; 95, 609 and 613; 2001, 3, 5; 17, 76; 18, 87; 21, 115 and 116; 31, 174). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Juriidilised isikud vastutavad k&auml;esoleva seaduse kohaselt. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Legal persons are liable pursuant to this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui &otilde;iguserikkuja on juriidilise isiku ametiisik, v&otilde;ib selle rikkumise asjas m&auml;&auml;rata karistuse samaaegselt f&uuml;&uuml;silisele isikule ja juriidilisele isikule seadusega etten&auml;htud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If the offender is an official of a legal person, the punishment for the offence may be imposed simultaneously on the natural person and the legal person pursuant to the procedure prescribed by law. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 26. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 26. </inglise>
<eesti>P&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitav m&auml;rgistamine isiku poolt, kellel puudub selleks &otilde;igus </eesti>
<inglise>Labelling of agricultural produce and products with reference to organic production methods by persons who have no right to do so </inglise>
<eesti>P&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitava m&auml;rgistamise eest juriidilise isiku poolt, kellel ei ole sellekohast &otilde;igust - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 100 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>If a legal person labels agricultural produce or products with a reference to organic production methods without having the right to do so, a fine of up to 100 000 kroons is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 27. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 27. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;uete rikkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Violation of requirements of organic plant production </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku taimekasvatuse n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest juriidilise isiku poolt - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 50 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>If a legal person violates the requirements of organic plant production, a fine of up to 50 000 kroons is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 28. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 28. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse n&otilde;uete rikkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Violation of requirements of organic livestock production </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku loomakasvatuse n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest juriidilise isiku poolt - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 50 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>If a legal person violates the requirements of organic livestock production, a fine of up to 50 000 kroons is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 29. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 29. </inglise>
<eesti>Mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise n&otilde;uete rikkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Violation of organic processing requirements </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;rgistatud p&otilde;llumajandussaaduse v&otilde;i -toote mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest juriidilise isiku poolt - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 100 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>If a legal person violates the requirements on the organic processing of labelled agricultural produce and products, a fine of up to 100 000 kroons is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 30. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 30. </inglise>
<eesti>Juriidilise isiku haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise asja menetlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Proceedings of matters concerning administrative offences of legal persons </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-des 26 kuni 29 nimetatud haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste asjades on &otilde;igus asja arutada ja karistus m&auml;&auml;rata: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The following have the right to hear administrative offence matters specified in &sect;&sect; 26 to 29 of this Act and to impose punishments: </inglise>
<eesti>1) Taimetoodangu Inspektsiooni peadirektoril ja tema aset&auml;itjal; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the Director General of the Plant Production Inspectorate and his or her deputy; </inglise>
<eesti>2) Veterinaar- ja Toiduameti peadirektoril, tema aset&auml;itjal, kohaliku asutuse juhil ja tema poolt volitatud j&auml;relevalveametnikul; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the Director General of the Veterinary and Food Board, his or her deputy, heads of local agencies of the Veterinary and Food Board, and officials carrying out inspections and authorised thereby; </inglise>
<eesti>3) Tervisekaitseinspektsiooni peadirektoril, tema aset&auml;itjal, kohaliku asutuse juhil ja tema aset&auml;itjal; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the Director General of the Health Protection Inspectorate, his or her deputy, heads of local agencies of the Health Protection Inspectorate and their deputies; </inglise>
<eesti>4) maa- v&otilde;i linnakohtu kohtunikul. </eesti>
<inglise>4) county or city court judges. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 punktides 1 kuni 3 nimetatud ametnikel on &otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;rata rahatrahv kuni 10 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Officials specified in clauses (1) 1) to 3) of this section have the right to impose fines of up to 10 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>Sellest suurema rahatrahvi v&otilde;ib m&auml;&auml;rata maa- v&otilde;i linnakohtu kohtunik. </eesti>
<inglise>Fines exceeding this amount may be imposed by county or city court judges. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-des 26 kuni 29 nimetatud haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste asjades on protokolli koostamise &otilde;igus: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The following have the right to prepare reports concerning administrative offence matters specified in &sect;&sect; 26 to 29 of this Act: </inglise>
<eesti>1) Taimetoodangu Inspektsiooni peadirektoril, tema aset&auml;itjal ja j&auml;relevalveametnikul; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the Director General of the Plant Production Inspectorate, his or her deputy and officials carrying out inspections; </inglise>
<eesti>2) Veterinaar- ja Toiduameti peadirektoril, tema aset&auml;itjal, kohaliku asutuse juhil ja j&auml;relevalveametnikul; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the Director General of the Veterinary and Food Board, his or her deputy, heads of local agencies of the Veterinary and Food Board and officials carrying out inspections; </inglise>
<eesti>3) Tervisekaitseinspektsiooni peadirektoril, tema aset&auml;itjal, kohaliku asutuse juhil, tema aset&auml;itjal ja j&auml;relevalveametnikul. </eesti>
<inglise>3) the Director General of the Health Protection Inspectorate, his or her deputy, heads of local agencies of the Health Protection Inspectorate, their deputies and officials carrying out inspections. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Juriidilise isiku &otilde;iguserikkumise asja menetletakse haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Matters concerning administrative offences committed by legal persons shall be heard pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Code of Administrative Offences. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 31. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 31. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise protokoll </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative offence reports </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Protokollis m&auml;rgitakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A report shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) koostamise aeg ja koht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the time and place of preparation; </inglise>
<eesti>2) j&auml;relevalveasutuse nimetus ja aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the name and address of the competent inspection authority; </inglise>
<eesti>3) protokolli koostanud isiku ees- ja perekonnanimi ning ametinimetus; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the given name, surname and official title of the person who prepares the report; </inglise>
<eesti>4) juriidilisest isikust &otilde;iguserikkuja nimi ja aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the name and address of the offender who is a legal person; </inglise>
<eesti>5) &otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja ees- ja perekonnanimi ning ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the given name, surname and position of the representative of the offender; </inglise>
<eesti>6) &otilde;iguserikkumise aeg ja koht ning rikkumise kirjeldus; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the time, place and description of the offence; </inglise>
<eesti>7) viide k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvile, mis n&auml;eb ette vastutuse selle &otilde;iguserikkumise eest; </eesti>
<inglise>7) a reference to the section of this Act which prescribes liability for the given offence; </inglise>
<eesti>8) tunnistajate seletused, ekspertiisi ja anal&uuml;&uuml;si andmed ning muu &otilde;iguserikkumist t&otilde;endav materjal; </eesti>
<inglise>8) statements by witnesses, information concerning expert opinions and analyses, and other materials which prove the commission of the offence; </inglise>
<eesti>9) &otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja seletus ja m&auml;rge, et talle on tutvustatud &otilde;igust kasutada &otilde;igusabi; </eesti>
<inglise>9) an explanation from the representative of the offender and a notation that he or she has been advised of the right to obtain legal assistance; </inglise>
<eesti>10) vajaduse korral muud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>10) other information as required. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Protokollile kirjutavad alla selle koostanud ametnik ja &otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The official who prepares the report and the representative of the offender shall sign the report. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui &otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja keeldub protokollile alla kirjutamast, tehakse selle kohta protokolli m&auml;rge. </eesti>
<inglise>If the representative of the offender refuses to sign the report, a corresponding notation shall be made in the report. </inglise>
<eesti>Protokollile lisatakse &otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja kirjalikud m&auml;rkused protokolli ja sellele allakirjutamisest keeldumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>Written comments of the representatives of the offender on the report and the refusal to sign the report shall be annexed to the report. </inglise>
