<eesti>Mahem&auml;rgi kasutuslubade kehtivus </eesti>
<inglise>Period of validity of ecolabel authorisation </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajal kehtivat mahem&auml;rgi kasutusluba omava tootja v&otilde;i k&auml;itleja ettev&otilde;te loetakse tunnustatuks k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise p&auml;evast arvates ja andmed kantakse mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registrisse mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa v&auml;ljaandja esitatud andmete ja isiku kirjaliku n&otilde;usoleku alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An enterprise of a producer or handler who has been granted ecolabel authorisation which is in force at the time of the entry into force of this Act is deemed to have been approved as of the date of the entry into force of this Act and the information is entered in the register of organic farming on the basis of the information submitted by the issuer of ecolabel authorisation and with the written permission of the person. </inglise>
<eesti>Nimetatud isikud v&otilde;ivad mahep&otilde;llumajandusele viitaval m&auml;rgistamisel kasutada seni kehtinud n&otilde;uetele vastavat mahem&auml;rki kuni 2001. aasta 31. detsembrini. </eesti>
<inglise>Such persons may use the ecolabel which is in compliance with the requirements currently in force when labelling with a reference to organic production methods until 31 December 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tootja puhul, kes on enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist asunud mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku toidu tootmise &uuml;leminekuperioodile, loetakse &uuml;leminekuaja alguseks seni kehtinud mahep&otilde;llumajanduse seaduse (RT I 1997, 51, 823; 1999, 30, 415; 2000, 40, 252) alusel mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa v&auml;ljaandja m&auml;rgitud &uuml;leminekuperioodi alguse kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In the case of producers who have entered the conversion period to the production of organic foodstuffs prior to the entry into force of this Act, the commencement of the conversion period is deemed to be the date of commencement of the conversion period as specified by the issuer of the ecolabel authorisation as provided for in the Organic Farming Act (RT I 1997, 51, 823; 1999, 30, 415; 2000, 40, 252) currently in force. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettev&otilde;te loetakse tunnustatuks ja andmed kantakse mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registrisse mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa v&auml;ljaandja esitatud andmete ja isiku kirjaliku n&otilde;usoleku alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>An enterprise is deemed to have been approved and the information is entered in the register of organic farming on the basis of the information submitted by the issuer of ecolabel authorisation and with the written permission of the person. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates &uuml;he kuu jooksul annavad mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa v&auml;ljaandjad Taimetoodangu Inspektsioonile &uuml;le dokumendid ja elektroonilise andmebaasi mahep&otilde;llumajandusliku toidu tootmise &uuml;leminekuperioodil olevate ja mahem&auml;rgi kasutusluba omavate isikute ning nende &uuml;le seni kehtinud mahep&otilde;llumajanduse seaduse alusel ja korras teostatud kontrolli ja mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa v&auml;ljaandja &uuml;le tehtud j&auml;relevalve kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Within one month after the entry into force of this Act, the issuers of ecolabel authorisation shall transfer to the Plant Production Inspectorate documents and an electronic database concerning persons undergoing the conversion period to the production of organic foodstuffs and persons with ecolabel authorisation, concerning monitoring of the persons performed on the basis of and pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Organic Farming Act currently in force, and concerning inspection of the issuers of ecolabel authorisation. </inglise>
<eesti>2001. aastal esitatud mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa taotlused koos lisadega antakse &uuml;le 10 p&auml;eva jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>Applications for ecolabel authorisation submitted during 2001 together with the annexes thereto shall be transferred within ten days after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Mahem&auml;rgi kasutusloa v&auml;ljaandjate poolt Taimetoodangu Inspektsioonile &uuml;leantavate dokumentide loetelu ja &uuml;leandmise korra ning k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1 ja 2 nimetatud tootjate ja k&auml;itlejate andmete mahep&otilde;llumajanduse registrisse kandmise korra kehtestab p&otilde;llumajandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The list of documents which the issuers of ecolabel authorisation are to transfer to the Plant Production Inspectorate, the procedure for transfer thereof, and the procedure for entry in the register of information concerning producers and handlers specified in subsections 1) and 2) of this section shall be established by the Minister of Agriculture. </inglise>
